long_description: we are reaching asia by supporting, training and encouraging asian believers to share the powerful gospel of jesus within their own cultures. over 3 billion people remain totally unreached by the gospel, and over 75% of them live in asia. we partner with indigenous church planters, evangelists and organisations to bring the good news of jesus to unreached people groups and support the growth of the church across asia. that is why we are enabling the translation, printing and distribution of bibles and christian books for believers across asia who have no access to scripture in their heart language. we believe that nobody reaches asians better than asians, and so we are passionate about empowering local believers to reach their own communities. through training, finances and practical support we enable them to pioneer outreach projects, communicating jesus in a way which is relevant to their culture. we seek to live out the power of jesus by blessing the poor through food and medical relief, education and vocational training.
